metadata.name: Api::V1::Accounts::FollowingAccountsController GET #index when requesting user is the account owner returns all accounts, including muted accounts

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "mutes" WHERE "mutes"."account_id" = $1 AND "mutes"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3

SELECT DISTINCT "follows"."id" AS alias_0, "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" LEFT OUTER JOIN "follows" ON "follows"."target_account_id" = "accounts"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "account_stats" ON "account_stats"."account_id" = "accounts"."id" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY "follows"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
